Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.59,0:00:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直棒出来的话  会如何做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立直棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真是坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会变成增加1000点对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.48,0:00:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  这样要达成正负0点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要打出4100点到5000点之间的点数
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.77,0:00:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  必须是70符2番
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够避开我的立直  把40符3番变成70符2番么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.86,0:00:38.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用70符2番来和是需要运气的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.63,0:00:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配这个空间的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.82,0:00:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人般的强运！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岭上开花自摸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,70符2番是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.49,0:01:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲家1200点  庄家2300点
