Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}只要觉得开心就会胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:13.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\be1}很好{\ropj}！{\r}　my mine Mind
